</P>
<P>
 Mission Viejo 213, Laguna Hills 236, Foothill 242 -- Jeff Cook was the 
medalist for Mission Viejo (5-4) with a two-over-par 38. Teammate Pat McCoy 
shot 40. Laguna Hills (2-4) finished second, followed by Foothill (2-5) at 
Mission Viejo Country Club. 
