Hastings * ** 569 49.0 Jim Klisanin ** 475 40.9 Charles Antos 118 10.1 District 
3 04,17,21,07,04 100% Precincts Reporting Votes % Gwen Forsythe * 811 63.9 John 
Baker 320 25.2 Kathy Parker 139 10.9 District 5 04,20,21,07,04 100% Precincts 
Reporting Votes % William J. Doane * 460 54.8 Richard Davies 380 45.2 Turnout: 
