<TEXT>
<P>
 OC High asks: What bugs you most about computers? What do you like best about 
them?  
</P>
<P>
 Responses gathered by Joslin Gemsch, Capistrano Valley; Koreen Kalie, 
Westminster; Michelle Pham, Trabuco Hills; Linda Dao, Los Amigos; Jessica Ming, 
Orange Lutheran; Laurel Gorman, Mission Viejo; Kai Wang, Anaheim; Jenifer 
Tobkin, Villa Park; Judy Tsai, Huntington Beach; Robert Wenzel, Irvine; Presida 
Brasov, Garden Grove; Eve Winnick, Loara; Amanda Garcia, El Modena; Cherie 
Chan, Marina; Luke Fenchel, University; Tricia Michels, Fountain Valley; Tori 
Clive, Cypress.  
